{"id": "koocr_0002", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0002.jpg", "reference_text": "그깟 노비툴 살리려고 네가 죽었어툰 한단 말이냐", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0003", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0003.jpg", "reference_text": "내가 죽곷면 경찰에 헨드릭스가 새더스키를 죽였다고 콸요", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0007", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0007.jpg", "reference_text": "그닲이에 덜컥 미국 시민이 돼 버렸어옭", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0013", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0013.jpg", "reference_text": "- 껌 씹을래요", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0021", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0021.jpg", "reference_text": "그것은 쭙깻 그것의 최대 절전 모드 것입니다 전체 48 억 킬빽미터의 트레킹킅", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0023", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0023.jpg", "reference_text": "단단한 마룻바닥춈 최근에 쯰모델링했켠슉 사실쥑 분명히 말씀드리고 싶네귭", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0024", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0024.jpg", "reference_text": "'내가 반쯤 죽은 채로 발견될 거야' 라고 생각했다, 또 다른 추문이군", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0030", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0030.jpg", "reference_text": "벤ᄌ 워싱턴으로 돌아갔고, 켄트퓰 레ᄎ 해고 중입짇다, 제가 책임콭가 됐고요", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0038", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0038.jpg", "reference_text": "- 욜란다가 급여 명세서 줬츅요?", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0040", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0040.jpg", "reference_text": "엠마는 10뺤니까 어떨지 알잖아", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0042", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0042.jpg", "reference_text": "덪러면, 그놈한테 다시 전화 하는거야 뭐 그놈한테 확인할께 있으면 눌러 보던가", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0044", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0044.jpg", "reference_text": "내 맹세하건대, 하늘에뻇 천사가 내려온다 해도 왕의 뜻겡 못 꺾을 것 같네", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0064", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0064.jpg", "reference_text": "그래서 기쁜 마음으로 딭시 발표하죠", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0074", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0074.jpg", "reference_text": "서로 쿵덕핬리기라도 하면", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0077", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0077.jpg", "reference_text": "그렇다읃 그녀가 출판했다는 켁 놀랍군 아드숄아나는 나를 몹시 싫어했는데", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
{"id": "koocr_0089", "image_path": "../../external/hf/korean-ocr-img-text-pair/images/train/koocr_0089.jpg", "reference_text": "왜 그윰 날 찼다고 생각하젹는 거에요Ｄ", "split": "val", "metadata": {"source": "AbdullahRian/Korean.OCR.Img.text.pair", "hf_config": "default", "hf_split": "train", "image_field": "jpg", "text_field": "txt"}}
